	<!-- Race Description -->
	<race name="Lunatic" desc="This unusual species shows thought patterns remarkably different from that of any other known race. Even after having evolved to a state that allows the utilization of higher brain functions, this race remained largely feral in their behavior. Simply put, they do not fight for abstract concepts such as honor but for the sheer joy of it.
	
	Though relying on instincts on many occasions, this species should not be underestimated. Their ships, while often having one glaring weakness or another, are always focussed towards reaching a specific goal; their unquestioned dedication to this goal makes them highly effective at one specific task.
	
	In terms of weaponry, this race employs many different technologies. Due to their specialized nature it is advised to disable and analyze their designs with scanning devices to allow for effective counters."/>
